OL,3,CRapist jailed for 13 years for child
OL,4,Csexual offences
OL,6,FA man from Somerset who raped a
OL,7,Fteenager has been jailed.
OL,9,FAaron Roberts, from Paulton, was found
OL,10,Fguilty of two sexual offences by a
OL,11,Fjury committed against a girl a few
OL,12,Fyears ago.
OL,14,FHe was sentenced at Bristol Crown
OL,15,FCourt on Monday 21 October, with the
OL,16,Fjudge saying an extended sentence was
OL,17,Fnecessary to protect the public.
