OL,6,FThe victim in the case provided a
OL,7,Fstatement to the court to explain the
OL,8,Fimpact Roberts' offending continues to
OL,9,Fhave on her.
OL,11,FShe said: "Emotionally, the crime you
OL,12,Fcommitted has torn me into pieces.
OL,13,FNever in my life have I ever felt so
OL,14,Fisolated and alone.
OL,16,F"My friendship group disappeared as
OL,17,Fthey were happy, innocent, naive
OL,18,Fchildren; I was a child when you took
OL,19,Fmy life away.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/7
