OL,4,Csexual offences
OL,6,F"They couldn't understand or
OL,7,Fcomprehend the trauma I suffered and
OL,8,Fstill am suffering. I had no friends.
OL,9,FI feel like an alien in society with a
OL,10,Fsign on my head and everyone is
OL,11,Flooking at me, pointing and talking
OL,12,Fabout me.
OL,14,F"You have ripped my world apart and
OL,15,Fevery bit of my life has been touched
OL,16,Fand I don't know how I will ever get
OL,17,Fover this and get some sort of normal
OL,18,Flife back.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/7
