OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax     F435A1729710550
OL,3,CRapist jailed for 13 years for child
OL,4,Csexual offences
OL,6,F"There is one word that I use to
OL,7,Fdescribe how you have left me feeling,
OL,8,Fpowerless. I am angry with myself that
OL,9,Fyou have made me feel that way."
OL,11,FShe also recognised the incredible
OL,12,Fsupport she has had from her family
OL,13,Fover the past few years.
OL,15,FRoberts was found guilty of one count
OL,16,Fof rape and a second of sexual
OL,17,Fassault. He also pleaded guilty to
OL,18,Fsexual activity in the presence of a
OL,19,Fchild relating to a separate matter
OL,20,Finvolving a different victim.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/7
