OL,6,FJudge Euan Ambrose handed Roberts a 13-
OL,7,Fyear prison sentence and will be
OL,8,Fsubject to a 10-year extended licence
OL,9,Fupon release. Roberts will also be on
OL,10,Fthe Sex Offenders' Register for life.
OL,12,FJudge Ambrose said: "It is impossible
OL,13,Fnot be moved by the suffering that you
OL,14,Fhave caused to the victim and her
OL,15,Ffamily.
OL,17,F"I have assessed that you pose a
OL,18,Fsignificant risk to members of the
OL,19,Fpublic and an extended sentence is
OL,20,Fappropriate."
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/7
