OL,6,F"By coming forward and testifying in
OL,7,Fcourt, she has without a doubt
OL,8,Fprotected others in the community from
OL,9,FRoberts' predatory and abhorrent
OL,10,Fbehaviour."
OL,12,FHe added "We hope this sentence can
OL,13,Fhelp her manage, and one day heal, the
OL,14,Ftrauma she still faces, as well as
OL,15,Fbring confidence to others who have
OL,16,Fbeen a victim of rape and sexual
OL,17,Foffences to come forward and report to
OL,18,Fthe police, knowing we will do
OL,19,Feverything in our power to get justice
OL,20,Ffor them."
